  "elapsed_s": 223.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had a pretty good general knowledge of the tragedy that was-- that have befallen, by that time, most of Central and Eastern European Jewry and-- and that was awaiting us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In part, that came from simple political consciousness and from following events and from being aware of the world that we lived in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was also buttressed by several [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bits of reliable information-- as reliable as you could get and as much as you could get.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, after the Polish debacle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At one point, we opened these borders for the Polish army to traverse Hungary after they surrendered their weapons.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had managed to, when they were coming across, to contact and spirit away some of the Jewish-- Polish Jewish solders, who had pretty good information on the atrocities that have already taken place.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was in the very early days, but it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, bits of information basically filtered through, even through that-- that thick curtain that was drawn around each of the occupied countries and-- or, for that money, each of the Axis countries, and-- and certainly around the-- the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, you know, the Holocaust was no secret, in essence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Either to the Jews or to the world at large.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And perhaps therein lies [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of the more serious elements of the tragedy, that despite the awareness, even if it wasn't quite accurate or the information was incomplete, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] nobody did what should have been done.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
